{"tid":1031193,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"為ipad PC化做準備！iOS、macOS 軟件即將於2021 合併！！！","createTime":"2019-02-21T13:00:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-23T14:44:24.000Z","uid":22675,"like":5,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"bded9b86c13081daad484058636a56815fd5a582","tid":1031193,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T13:00:48.000Z","msg":"發表時間：2019-02-21 07:02收錄檢舉<br />\n<br />\n \t<br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"https://timgm.eprice.com.hk/hk/mobile/img/2019-02/21/212417/uniqlo_1_f61fa32ac65e1717f715d013e39253cd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftimgm.eprice.com.hk%2Fhk%2Fmobile%2Fimg%2F2019-02%2F21%2F212417%2Funiqlo_1_f61fa32ac65e1717f715d013e39253cd.jpg&h=49c4a9b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一直有傳 Apple 會將 iOS 和 Mac 的軟件整合，昨日彭博通訊社報導指，這個代號 Marzipan 的合併計劃將會在今年 6 月舉行的 WWDC 全球開發者大會正式公佈。Apple 打算首先讓開發者將 iPad 程式移植到 Mac，然後再在 2020 年將計劃延展至 iPhone 程式。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nApple 將 iPhone、iPad 和 Mac 程式整合的終極目標，到了 2021 年就會完成，開發者毋須為不同平台重新編寫軟件的程式碼，亦不再需要將軟件分別向 Apple 旗下幾個 App Store 呈交。Marzipan 計劃並非將 iOS 和 macOS 合併，而是透過軟件包方式讓開發者可以製作跨平台的程式，這或許可以令現時一池死水的 macOS App Store 回復生機。<br />\n<br />\n有關將 iOS 和 Mac 軟件整合的消息早在 2017 年開始傳出，去年 6 月舉行的 WWDC，Apple 展示了一系列以全新 UIkit 套件，基於 iOS 新聞、股票、家居和語音備忘而開發的 Mac 軟件，當時 Apple 表示跟 UIkit 相同的功能會在 2019 年向第三方開發者提供。"},{"pid":"6f3f07d2e5309916885dec6c0ccb5f7d10756205","tid":1031193,"uid":201464,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T13:04:36.000Z","msg":"Arm 同 x86 同一os？"},{"pid":"b63467089588735b9d312579a2bfbb17ce12092b","tid":1031193,"uid":15564,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T13:06:16.000Z","msg":"咁我2021年先買ipad囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7059023f58474bed9b5264bbf6a95bae2b0d14fe","tid":1031193,"uid":22675,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"6f3f07d2e5309916885dec6c0ccb5f7d10756205","tid":1031193,"uid":201464,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T13:04:36.000Z","msg":"Arm 同 x86 同一os？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T13:08:34.000Z","msg":"錯，arm版mac"},{"pid":"643fdafcb4ac20249d73b9af18d0548194aa5a2d","tid":1031193,"uid":41308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7059023f58474bed9b5264bbf6a95bae2b0d14fe","tid":1031193,"uid":22675,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"6f3f07d2e5309916885dec6c0ccb5f7d10756205","tid":1031193,"uid":201464,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T13:04:36.000Z","msg":"Arm 同 x86 同一os？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T13:08:34.000Z","msg":"錯，arm版mac"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T13:09:53.000Z","msg":"咁我仲買mac做乜？"},{"pid":"6fd7382024db88680f0afcd7a9e27d7b4ed96fac","tid":1031193,"uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"643fdafcb4ac20249d73b9af18d0548194aa5a2d","tid":1031193,"uid":41308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7059023f58474bed9b5264bbf6a95bae2b0d14fe","tid":1031193,"uid":22675,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"6f3f07d2e5309916885dec6c0ccb5f7d10756205","tid":1031193,"uid":201464,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T13:04:36.000Z","msg":"Arm 同 x86 同一os？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T13:08:34.000Z","msg":"錯，arm版mac"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T13:09:53.000Z","msg":"咁我仲買mac做乜？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T13:13:06.000Z","msg":"就係想你唔好買"},{"pid":"00bcde0a7448c9829383f184b725d03c79014cda","tid":1031193,"uid":1130,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T14:06:34.000Z","msg":"不如傳埋steve jobs出年復活"},{"pid":"f643a29dd7fff3ba76ffb6d8d359b1ddf4e55293","tid":1031193,"uid":226155,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T14:08:52.000Z","msg":"上年唔係話mac上面用到iOS apps咩，點解變成ipad pc化？"},{"pid":"9971e8e3d052e717e9fa481f335faef2f3cc0f7a","tid":1031193,"uid":15831,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T14:14:48.000Z","msg":"唔係合併<br />\n<br />\niPad 亦唔會一體化<br />\n<br />\n個 project 所指既成係統一 iOS 同 macOS 既底層 api <br />\n統一左唔等於 macOS 用到所有 iOS app <br />\n只係 developer 寫多個 macOS 版既時候唔洗由底寫起禁浪費時間<br />\n同埋一啲 iOS 已經好 popular 既 framework 可以係 macOS 共用"},{"pid":"9c4708fb4776a22ddfee028c871b9f528d4020f5","tid":1031193,"uid":165187,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T14:16:39.000Z","msg":"生果已完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ad10ed1ac64c65ed0623340c841d73ad5a155be","tid":1031193,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T07:50:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e35859e78e357b27e603e7742b87490d71c34d2","tid":1031193,"uid":19609,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T12:05:59.000Z","msg":"唔係ipad pc 化<br />\n而係mac ipad 化<br />\n<br />\n本身mac 個app store 就係垃圾<br />\n佢想將iphone ipad d app 移殖去mac app store, 睇落冇咁廢<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nmac 上面既photoshop ai 呢d 唔會係ipad 用到"},{"pid":"611fbb1aa513428f14f6abdd600bfff899eeb412","tid":1031193,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T05:40:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1e04f29783195d65532876376b2df263f8bcb96","tid":1031193,"uid":18753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"00bcde0a7448c9829383f184b725d03c79014cda","tid":1031193,"uid":1130,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T14:06:34.000Z","msg":"不如傳埋steve jobs出年復活"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T13:27:47.000Z","msg":"傳Steve jobs已經復活，但佢決定等apple 衰落先再肯出山<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8fcff325a014a3fa2f1ce4330e57f455c40c47c","tid":1031193,"uid":68094,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T14:44:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}